
The dividend and divisor are defined at assembly time in the .data
section of divide.s.

REQUIREMENTS

  - GNU Assembler (as) 2.30+
  - GNU Linker (ld) 2.30+
  - Linux x86-64

BUILDING

  $ make

LIMITATIONS

  - Outputs quotient only (no remainder)
  - Division by zero causes SIGFPE
  - Maximum output: 10 digits (2^31-1)

